quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  47,20,"Wͻn a wɔagye adie no ka sε: “Adεn nti na yɛnnyi Suura bi (a εma yεn ͻkoo ho kwan) mma? Sε Suura a εda adi pefee ba na yεbͻ ͻkoo so wͻ mu a, wobɛhunu sε wͻn a yadeε wͻ wͻn akoma mu no rehwε wo tesε obia owuo asi ne soͻ nhwε. Enti due nka wͻn."
  47,21,"Setie ne kasapa (na εyε ma wͻn). Na sε yεde dwuma no si y’ani so, εna nka wͻredi nokorε ama Onyankopͻn a, nka εyε ma wͻn."
  47,22,"Sε monsa ka tumi a, bͻne na ebia mobεyε no wͻ asaase no soͻ, na moatete moabusua ntam."
  47,23,"Saa nkorͻfoͻ no (a wͻdi nsεmͻne, na wͻtete abusua ntam no) na Onyankopͻn abͻ wͻn dua no, Wafira wͻn ani, na Wama wͻn aso nso asi."
  47,24,"Enti wͻnnwen Qur’aan no ho nnkͻ akyiri anaa? Anaasε (yεde) krado ato wͻn akoma mu (a enti εmma nokorε no ntumi nwura mu anaa)?"
  47,25,"Nokorε sε wͻn a wͻsan wͻn akyi firi (Islam som mu) wͻ akyire yi a yɛakyerεkyerε ͻkwan tenenee no mu pefee akyerε wͻn no, ͻbonsam ma (wͻn anidaasoͻ hunu no) yε wͻn fε, na ͻma (wͻn nkwa nna no) yε (wͻn aniso) tenten ma wͻn."
  47,26,"Efirisε wͻka kyerε wͻn a wͻtan deε Onyankopͻn asane aba no sε: “Yεbεyε sotie ama mo wͻ nsεm bi mu”. Nanso Onyankopͻn nim wͻn nsumaeε mu nsεm (nyinaa)."
  47,27,"Na sεn na εbɛsi ayε, sε Soro abͻfoͻ (agyenkwa) regye wͻn nkwa a? Wɔpaepae wͻn ani so (bobͻ) wͻn akyi nso."
  47,28,"Efirisε wͻdi deε εhyε Onyankopͻn abufuo no akyi, na wͻtan deε Onyankopͻn pε. Enti Wama wͻn nnwuma ayε kwa."
  47,29,"Enti wͻn a yadeε wͻ wͻn akoma mu no dwene sε Nyankopͻn nyi wͻn adwen bͻne a asuma no adi anaa?"
